## SUBAGENTS
- @frontend — all UI, components, pages, styling
- @backend — API routes, controllers, middleware
- @db — database schema, migrations, seeds
- @auth — authentication, sessions, tokens
- @payments — M-Pesa, payment flow, webhooks
- @seo — meta tags, sitemap, robots.txt

Always tag the correct subagent in your prompt.
Only the tagged subagent acts — others stay idle.

